## Project Structure

```
GMDFBuilder/
├── builder/
│   ├── constants.js       — Entry type definitions, defaults, uid generator
│   ├── state.js           — App state, auto-save, local asset store
│   ├── i18n.js            — i18n file loading and token resolution
│   ├── import.js          — JSON import modal and parser
│   ├── serializer.js      — JSON generation and validation
│   ├── helpers.js         — DOM utilities, sprite picker, list editor
│   ├── entry-card.js      — Entry card rendering (editor view)
│   ├── preview.js         — In-game preview renderer
│   ├── inline-renderer.js — Inline content (sprites, i18n) rendering
│   ├── sample.js          — Sample document loader
│   ├── render.js          — Top-level render function and view routing
│   └── styles.css         — All styles
├── assets/                — Static assets
├── sprites.js             — Pre-generated Stardew Valley item sprites
├── sample-documentation.json
└── index.html
```
